{"tid":1366190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真一問點解727元朗遊行係非法？","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T03:02:49.000Z","uid":260654,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ed4812e498cfbe5f95090d1a65f9f7e4921a0f07","tid":1366190,"uid":260654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:30:00.000Z","msg":"基本法賦予咗香港人遊行集會結社出版新聞等自由，根本每次遊行都唔需要同警方申請。如果要警察政府批准，咁新聞出版要唔要每次出之前都問過政府呢單新聞上唔上得報、呢本書出唔出得街啊？<br />\n頭先聽晴朗居然兩個主持人都話星期六個遊行係非法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打電話上去嗰個元朗居民又係膠嘅，俾主持咁樣講一講就怯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不反對通知書個名又係好誤導，即係俾個位警察政府去反對。<br />\n根本只係應該叫遊行通知書就算，遞交俾警察只係告知警方有呢個遊行，等佢哋安排人手同封路。<br />\n就算所謂嘅公安條例都唔可以同基本法嘅大前提有衝突。<br />\n如果大家有更正確嘅說法請告知小妹，多謝。"},{"pid":"5e709441c0d126891fdf7b2a5cc4322026b5d2f2","tid":1366190,"uid":260654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W7Dj36R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW7Dj36R.png&h=581d0007&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d68fd810b8c0b823390c65ce1c9c66c461549e95","tid":1366190,"uid":260654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"61acd79661a4b3ce644123883029413b887b333b","tid":1366190,"uid":260654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:33:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6501e562e2b75abcc40a36fd19b2b29e92834b08","tid":1366190,"uid":269659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbywaNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpbywaNE.jpg&h=f68cefcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fdba35f962366a1f9d88756c508d176416578fb","tid":1366190,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cla